            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis thus that we must come today"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To worship in reality:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When we bring Christ as produce sweet"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God fully satisfied will be."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The worship that God so desired"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Was not with manna sent from heav’n,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But from their labor on the land"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The people’s gifts to God were giv’n."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus, what God so desires today."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Are not the miracles so grand,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But daily, normal life in Christ,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As worship, produce of the land."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The manna came from God alone;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The produce, from man’s work on Him."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So all our worship now must come"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From mingling with the Lord within."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As day by day we live in Christ,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And take Him as our everything,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The produce of the land comes forth"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And worship true to God we’ll bring."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The manna, Lord, no more we’ll seek,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But Christ in all we will apply;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then we will have some produce sweet,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thine own dear heart to satisfy."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    }
  ],
